To open delevoper tools:
Windows = Control + Shift + J
Mac = Command + Option + I

\*Variable creation:
let school = "SheCodes";
let fullPackage = "SheCodes Pro";
let projects = 4;
let awesome = true;

\*Variable operations
let x = 2;
let y = 3;
let z = x + y; // 5

let city = "Lisbon";
let country = "Portugal";
let place = city + " " + country; //Lisbon Portugal

\*Variable data types
let age = 23; // Number
let name = "Julie"; // String
let canCode = true; // Boolean, could also be false

\*Internal JavaScript

<body>
  <h1>
    SheCodes
  </h1>
  <script>
    alert("Hello SheCodes");
  </script>
</body>
Add your script tag to the bottom of your body. Anything inside script is JavaScript.

